Avaritia is amazing, just as I thought, mo.
It's full of people and so lively, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300023_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But there are some scary parts too, mo.
I bumped into a Superbian man earlier
and he glared at me, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300023_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Razzlydazzly ran for it as fast as I could, mo.
Once I put some distance between us,
he stopped chasing me, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300023_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Rex, you should use that as a reference
when you need to escape from an enemy, mo.
